  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA8-kiḷavi">iḵtiyaṟkaip puṇarcci yiṟutikkaṇ ṭalaimakaḷai yāyattoṭuṅ kaṇṭa talaimakaṉ colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is what HE said who saw HER together with [her] friends at the end of the natural union.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA8">
<l>            alkupaṭa ruḻanta varimatar maḻaikkaṭ</l>
<l>            palpūm pakaittaḻai nuṭaṅku malkuṟ</l>
<l>            ṟirumaṇi puraiyu mēṉi maṭavōḷ</l>
<l>            yārmakaḷ kolliva ṭantai vāḻiyar</l>
<l>            tuyara muṟīiyiṉa ḷemmē yakalvaya </l>
<l>            larivaṉa rarintun taruvaṉar peṟṟun</l>
<l>            taṇcēṟu tāya mataṉuṭai nōṉṟāṭ</l>
<l>            kaṇpō ṉeytal pōrviṟ pūkkun</l>
<l>            tiṇṭērp poṟaiyaṉ ṟoṇṭi</l>
<l>            taṉṟiṟam peṟukaviva ḷīṉṟa tāyē.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The inexperienced girl with a body resembling a radiant sapphire,</l>
        <l rend="indent">with hips where foliage is swaying in contrast<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">pakai taḻai</term>: explained by T.V.G. as leaf skirt joined together one leaf up, one down. See also KT 293.5.</note> with many flowers,</l>
        <l rend="indent">with red-streaked luxuriant rain eyes that suffered lasting affliction,</l>
        <l>– whose daughter is she?<note place="foot">Or: "who is [this] woman?"</note> May [her] father live.</l>
        <l>She has caused us grief.</l>
        <l rend="indent">May the mother, who begot her, obtain the opulence</l>
        <l rend="indent2">of Toṇṭi itself<note place="foot">Are we entitled to read <term xml:lang="ta">toṇṭi-taṉ tiṟam</term>, in spite of the line break?</note>, [the city] of Poṟaiyaṉ with firm chariot,</l>
        <l rend="indent3">where, as cutters cut [and] carriers receive [the harvest],</l>
        <l rend="indent4">blue waterlilies flower in [hay-]heaps like eyes,</l>
        <l rend="indent4">with beautiful strong stems, spread in the cool mud,</l>
        <l rend="indent4">in the wide paddy field.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
          </body>
            </text>
